SUBENT        30470003   20260425   20260508   20260508       3222
BIB                  5         15
REACTION   (1-H-2(N,2N)1-H-1,,DA)
            for neutron emission.
ANALYSIS   (INTED)
COMMENT    The double differential cross-sections for neutron
            emissions were integrated with respect to energy.
           .For the extrapolation to 'zero' energy, it was assumed
            that the cross-sections fall linearly zero at 0 energy
            (This approximation agrees to the result by the theory
             of Aaron-Amade within the errors)
