BIB                  4         11
REACTION   (6-C-12(N,INL)6-C-12,PAR,DA)
COMMENT    Side experiment performed to check the present
            measurements of deuteron break-up cross-section.
           At 14.8 MeV of neutron energy, reaction A,
           .(A) 12C+n =  9*Be+a = 3a+n
           can be neglected and only reaction B occurs.
           .(B) 12C+n = 12*C+a = 3a+n'.
STATUS     (TABLE,,K.Gul+,J,JP/G,5,1107,1979) Table 2
